Class VehicleDTOBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.algonquin.www.common.builder.VehicleDTOBuilder
public class VehicleDTOBuilder extends Object
Builder class for constructing VehicleDTO objects using a fluent API.

This class simplifies the creation of VehicleDTO instances by allowing chained method calls to set various properties. 

 Example usage:
 VehicleDTO vehicle = new VehicleDTOBuilder()
     .id(1L)
     .vehicleNumber("BUS123")
     .vehicleType("Bus")
     .energyTYpe("Electric")
     .consumptionRate(15.5)
     .maxPassengers(50)
     .route("Route A")
     .status("Active")
     .build();
